lead_paragraph: Top-seeded John Isner had a two-set tournament-record 24 aces to knock out fellow American Denis Kudla 7-6 (2), 7-6 (4) in the second round of the U.S. men's clay court championships on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Isner Ousts Kudla at US Clay Court Championships
headline.main: Isner Ousts Kudla at US Clay Court Championships
